Class HystrixDelegatingRequestContext

  • java.lang.Object

    RequestContext

    public class HystrixDelegatingRequestContext
extends Object
implements RequestContext
    Delegated all RequestContex method calls to the contained delegate, while also initializing and shutting down a HystrixRequestContext as needed.
